Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.67,0:00:05.80,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(480,80)}They're called Riders.{NOTE:少年達はライダー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.80,0:00:08.34,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(480,80)}They are those who bond with monsters.{NOTE:モンスターと絆を結びし者たちである。}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.97,0:00:12.26,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Sky-High Extreme!{NOTE:「スカイエクストリーム」！}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.82,0:00:29.32,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{\an8}As expected from Navirou's disciple!{NOTE:さすがは、ナビルーの一番弟子！}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:31.62,Default,Deburi,0,0,0,,{\an8}That disciple of yours is pretty awesome!{NOTE:凄いぞ、お前の弟子は。}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.62,0:00:33.58,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ain't that right, ain't that right?{NOTE:そうだろう、そうだろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.08,0:00:42.13,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,It's alive!{NOTE:生きている！}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:47.17,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,No way.{NOTE:まさか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.30,0:00:51.26,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,You're the toughest Black One?{NOTE:お前が最凶の黒？}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.26,0:00:53.31,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,We'll take him on!{NOTE:俺たちが相手だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.57,0:01:09.66,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,The power of bonds won't yield to the Black Blight.{NOTE:絆の力は黒の凶気に屈しない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.66,0:01:11.37,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,That's why we…{NOTE:だから、俺たちは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:14.58,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,…won't lose to you!{NOTE:絶対に負けない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.05,0:01:35.35,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(480,80)}Lute and friends defeated the Black Blight and restored peace to the world.{NOTE:黒の凶気を終わらせ、世界に平和を取り戻したリュート達。}
