Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:23.11,Lyrics (EN),,0,0,0,,We are still living today{NOTE:僕ら今日も生きている}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:26.34,Lyrics (EN),,0,0,0,,We are still laughing today{NOTE:僕ら今日も笑ってる}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.34,0:02:30.84,Lyrics (EN),,0,0,0,,We don't need anything more{NOTE:それだけでもう何もいらない}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:32.71,Lyrics (EN),,0,0,0,,Just RIDE ON{NOTE:今すぐRIDE ON}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:36.01,Lyrics (EN),,0,0,0,,We're quick to want{NOTE:僕らすぐに求める}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:39.21,Lyrics (EN),,0,0,0,,This feeling is only natural{NOTE:欲張りな生き物さ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.21,0:02:45.24,Lyrics (EN),,0,0,0,,We're born without anything after all{NOTE:何も持たずに生まれてきたのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:47.01,Lyrics (EN),,0,0,0,,Happiness is{NOTE:幸せは}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:50.08,Lyrics (EN),,0,0,0,,To be by your side, to be close to you{NOTE:そばにあって　近くにあって}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:53.48,Lyrics (EN),,0,0,0,,Not to lose sight of what is really important{NOTE:大切なものほど見えなくなるけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:54.78,Lyrics (EN),,0,0,0,,To be grateful{NOTE:感謝して}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:59.81,Lyrics (EN),,0,0,0,,To the person who understands no matter what happens{NOTE:何が起きたって分かってくれる人へ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.81,0:03:02.81,Lyrics (EN),,0,0,0,,Everyone is afraid{NOTE:誰にだって　逃げたくなって}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.81,0:03:06.24,Lyrics (EN),,0,0,0,,To lose sight of oneself{NOTE:自分を見失いそうになるけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:14.21,Lyrics (EN),,0,0,0,,But you will surely find love in your heart{NOTE:愛は必ず君の心にあるよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:19.44,Lyrics (EN),,0,0,0,,Come walk with us{NOTE:僕ら一緒に歩いていこうよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:25.04,Lyrics (EN),,0,0,0,,We're under the same sky, we look at the same stars{NOTE:同じ空のした　同じ空を見上げながら}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:30.11,Lyrics (EN),,0,0,0,,Let's keep this beautifully colored bond{NOTE:美しい色の絆　数えていよう}
