Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:29.26,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(210,50)\fad(700,700)\fs40}Episode 50\N"A Strong and Dangerous\NMan Shrouded in Mystery"{NOTE:第50話\\N強く危ない謎の奴}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:29.93,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Now you should have an idea about our power.{NOTE:これで俺たちの実力を分かっちゃっただろ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:31.77,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Better be serious this time.{NOTE:次は本気で来い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:34.85,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Where's Avinia?{NOTE:アユリアはどこだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:37.23,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,That's not your concern.{NOTE:それはお前には関係ない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:41.07,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,I came here to obtain your Kinship Stone.{NOTE:俺はお前の絆石を取りにきたんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:42.94,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Why do you want it?{NOTE:何で俺の絆石を？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:45.03,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Cut the small talk!{NOTE:一々煩い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:50.62,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Ratha!{NOTE:レウス。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:57.46,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Pretty good.{NOTE:やるな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:04:58.23,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Ratha!{NOTE:レウス。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:09.26,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Ratha, are you okay?{NOTE:レウス、大丈夫か？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:14.73,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Why Rider raises a hand against another Rider?{NOTE:ライダーがライダーに武器を向けるとはどういうことだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:16.10,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,What?{NOTE:何だと？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:18.77,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,We're fighting… that?{NOTE:こいつは戦いなんだぜ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:20.15,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Let me say it again.{NOTE:もう一度言おう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:21.98,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Be serious this time.{NOTE:本気で来い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:25.03,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,I won't fight a Rider.{NOTE:ライダーはライダーに剣を向けたりしない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:26.95,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,That's just stupid.{NOTE:そんなものは意味がない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:29.16,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,You're right.{NOTE:知ってるさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:31.28,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,There's no meaning to it.{NOTE:意味なんて何にだってない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:39.08,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,But if that's your way of doing…{NOTE:だが、それがお前らの流儀だっていうなら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:40.63,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,…we will do it.{NOTE:合わせてやるよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:42.46,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,As expected from master Gale.{NOTE:さすがゲイル様。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:45.13,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,You're not like the others!{NOTE:他の方々とは一味違う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:47.72,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,And if we're to fight, I am going to win.{NOTE:合わせた上で俺が勝つ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:01.77,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Whew.{NOTE:お。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:03.48,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,What's with that Rathalos?{NOTE:リオレウス同士だ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:06.82,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Not only he can breathe fire, he's equally strong at it.{NOTE:炎を浴びせ合ってもお互い火には強いからな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:10.41,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Equally strong?{NOTE:お互いリオレウス同士だと？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:18.37,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Equally?{NOTE:お互い？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:26.21,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,What's with you?{NOTE:何なのだお前？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:27.76,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,You're creeping me out.{NOTE:感じ悪いな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:30.64,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,You're a disgrace to Airous.{NOTE:アイルーの風上にも置けないな。\\Nhttps://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%82%A2%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB%E3%83%BC}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:36.39,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Certainly Ratha is an ordinary species, and your Rathalos is special species.{NOTE:確かにレウスは普通のリオレウスで、お前のとこはリオレウス希少種だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:42.73,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,You may be stronger, but Lute and Ratha have a strong bond.{NOTE:モンスターとしての強さは上かもしれないが、リュートとレウスには絆の強さがあるのだぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:49.99,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Master Gale, he has no clue.{NOTE:ゲイル様。こいつら何も知りません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:52.87,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,You can't blame him.{NOTE:しかたがないな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:55.04,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Why don't we teach him the hard way?{NOTE:なら教えてやるかか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:57.00,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Dusk, let's use Thunder Strike.{NOTE:ダスク。龍光まといだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:05.09,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,What's with that glow?{NOTE:何だ、あの光は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:07.92,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,He just said Thunder Strike.{NOTE:だから「龍光まとい」だよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:11.47,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,"Thunder Strike" can be used only by Stygian Zinogres.{NOTE:「龍光まとい」はジンオウガ亜種が使うものだぞ。\\Nhttp://monsterhunter.wikia.com/wiki/Stygian_Zinogre}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:14.35,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,How a Rathalos could use it?{NOTE:何でリオレウスが龍光をまとうのだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:17.93,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,It's because we've awakened its sleeping bond gene.{NOTE:眠っていた絆遺伝子を目覚めさせたからさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:19.68,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,A bond gene?{NOTE:絆遺伝子?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:21.23,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,What's that?{NOTE:なんなのだそれは?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:24.23,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,You really know nothing, do you?{NOTE:お前ら本当に何も知らないな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:26.44,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,You don't even know about the Rite of Channeling.{NOTE:伝承の儀を知らないんだ。\\Nhttps://game8.jp/mh-stories/91329}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:28.65,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,So what if I don't know!{NOTE:はっきり言って知らない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:29.86,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Just tell us already!{NOTE:なんだそれは!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:35.41,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,If you awaken the bond genes, you can increase Monstie's abilities.{NOTE:だから絆遺伝子を目覚めさせて、オトモンの能力を増やすんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:41.75,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Hey, Rider. Try dodging this Dragon Breath!{NOTE:よ、ライダー君。拡散龍ブレスだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:47.71,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Dragon Breath?{NOTE:拡散龍ブレス？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:49.96,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Rathalos can't use such thing.{NOTE:リオレウスはそんなもの使えないぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:52.68,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,I wonder about that.{NOTE:それがそうじゃないんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:00.10,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Lute!{NOTE:リュート！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:02.98,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,I-I can't move!{NOTE:か、体が動かない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:05.15,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Ratha! Take him to safety!{NOTE:レウス！逃げるのだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:11.15,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Escaping, huh?{NOTE:逃すか、おい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:14.53,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Master Gale!{NOTE:あ、ゲイル様！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:23.92,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Lute!{NOTE:しっかりするのだリュート！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:26.75,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Hey!{NOTE:ほーら！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:28.50,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Looks like we caught up!{NOTE:追い付いちゃった！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:34.38,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Donuts?{NOTE:ドーナツ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:35.59,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Not that.{NOTE:間違えた！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:37.18,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Found it!{NOTE:こっちだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:40.97,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Where are you?{NOTE:どこだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:43.35,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,There! There! Take this!{NOTE:それ！それ！それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:45.02,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Dusk, go up!{NOTE:ダスク、上だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:48.15,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Tsk.{NOTE:チッ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:53.36,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Where are Lute and Navirou?{NOTE:リュートとナビちゃんどこ行っちゃったんだろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:56.28,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,We need to get ready for the departure.{NOTE:旅立ちの準備しなきゃならないのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:09:00.08,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Navirou can't be helped.{NOTE:ナビルーったらホントしょうがありませんね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.54,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Trouble!{NOTE:大変だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:03.04,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Hey!{NOTE:おぉい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:03.83,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Oh?{NOTE:お？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.83,0:09:05.50,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,What was that?{NOTE:何？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:09.21,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Emergency! It's an emergency!{NOTE:緊急事態！非常事態だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:10.38,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Lute!{NOTE:リュート！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:13.84,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Black Riders have appeared!{NOTE:ブラックライダーズが現れた!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:25.89,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Then he told Lute to give up his Kinship Stone and challenged him to a battle…{NOTE:それでそいつはリュートに絆石をよこせと言って戦いを挑んできて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:29.65,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,…then his Monstie could use very unusual abilities…{NOTE:…そいつの乗ってるオトモンは普通じゃない能力も使って…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:32.90,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,…and then they were babbling about some genes and ceremonies!{NOTE:絆遺伝子とか伝承の儀とか言って！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:34.74,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,You mean the Rite of Channeling?{NOTE:伝承の儀じゃと？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:36.45,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,What's that?{NOTE:何ですか、それは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:38.62,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,We have no time for explanation.{NOTE:説明している暇はない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:41.62,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,You need to locate the Channeler, Lute.{NOTE:伝承ジイさんの元へ行くのだリュート。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:43.83,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,Take Cheval with you.{NOTE:そしてシュヴァルもじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:45.62,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,The Channeler, hm?{NOTE:伝承ジイさんって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:48.46,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,It's a Wyverian living in the Darj Snowfields.{NOTE:タルジュ雪原にいる竜人じゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.46,0:09:51.63,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Isn't that where Riddlemaster lived?{NOTE:あれはなぞなぞジイさんではなかったのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:56.22,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,I guess he wasn't only about riddles.{NOTE:やっぱりあのじいさんただのなぞなぞ好きじゃなかったんだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:10:01.51,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,They're collecting Kinship Stones and use the Rite of Channeling.{NOTE:絆石を狙っているそやつが伝承の儀を使ったというのなら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:04.31,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,You should depart as soon as possible.{NOTE:…一刻も早く出発するのじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:06.31,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Master Gale.{NOTE:ゲイル様。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:08.31,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Master Gale!{NOTE:ゲイル様!}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:10.31,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Where are you?{NOTE:どこ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:12.23,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Don't slack!{NOTE:ぐずぐずしてんな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:13.07,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Hop in!{NOTE:乗れ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:14.86,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Yes sir!{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:16.13,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,Understand?{NOTE:よいな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:19.86,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,Meet the Channeler and listen to everything he says.{NOTE:伝承ジイさんに会って全てを聞くがよい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:21.41,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Leave the village to us.{NOTE:村の方は任せて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:23.91,Default,Chamo,0,0,0,,We'll keep watching over it without sleeping.{NOTE:寝ずに見張ってるでしゅニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:26.54,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, we'll be here.{NOTE:何かあっても僕たちがいるから！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:29.46,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,Focus on collecting the knowledge, purr.{NOTE:知恵を集めれば大丈夫だゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:32.13,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Good luck, Lute.{NOTE:リュート先輩、頑張ってください！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:35.88,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,House watching is pretty boring, but we'll take it on!{NOTE:留守番はつまんねえが引き受けてやるぜ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.88,0:10:37.05,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Well then, let's go.{NOTE:では行くぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:38.88,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:41.14,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Qurupeco!{NOTE:クルペッコ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:42.39,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:45.27,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,Monoblos!{NOTE:モノブロス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:46.47,Default,Stone,0,0,0,,Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:49.48,Default,Stone,0,0,0,,Gravios!{NOTE:グラビモス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:50.69,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:53.69,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Aptonoth!{NOTE:アプトノス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:54.82,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:58.49,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Rathian!{NOTE:リオレイア！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:01.41,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I will accompany you, Cheval!{NOTE:お供しますよシュヴァルさん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:03.37,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,All right, depart!{NOTE:よし！出発！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:13.50,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Lute?{NOTE:リュート？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:18.05,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,To save Avinia, we need to fight Black Riders.{NOTE:アユリアを助けるにはブラックライダーズと戦いになるだろうけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:20.68,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,That Rathalos was strange.{NOTE:…あのリオレウス普通じゃなかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:21.68,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Yep.{NOTE:うむ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:24.76,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,He used Thunder Strike like a Zinogre…{NOTE:ジンオウガ亜種のように龍光をまとい…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:28.22,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,…and fire Dragon Breath like a Deviljho!{NOTE:イビルジョーのように拡散龍ブレスを吐いたぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:30.02,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Even though it's a Rathalos.{NOTE:リオレウスなのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:31.98,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,What is the Rite of Channeling?{NOTE:伝承の儀って何だろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:35.40,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Is that supposed to change Ratha?{NOTE:それってレウスを変えちゃうってことなのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:38.32,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,For now, we can't know for sure.{NOTE:話を聞いてみないと分からないけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:41.45,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,But whatever it is, it won't change our bond.{NOTE:…俺たちとオトモンの絆は変わらないと思うよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:46.24,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,Dan.{NOTE:ダン先輩。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:48.49,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,We're pretty small in numbers.{NOTE:これだけの数のライダーがいるんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:50.62,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,Why don't we all go?{NOTE:全員で迎え撃ったらどうだろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.62,0:11:55.13,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's beat them up with all of us!{NOTE:そうか！全員でボッコボコにしてやる！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:59.21,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,But we are not used to fighting among Riders.{NOTE:だけど俺たちライダー同士で戦うのは慣れてないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:02.51,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,It's different from fighting against a monster.{NOTE:モンスター相手とは勝手が違うからな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:03.59,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Yep.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:07.68,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,He pulled out his sword and slashed Ratha with me on it.{NOTE:あいつ剣を抜いて俺とレウスに斬りつけてきたんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:09.85,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,He went that far?{NOTE:そんなことまでしてくるのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:12.14,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,That's bad.{NOTE:それは良くないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:14.60,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Also it is not just one person.{NOTE:それに向こうも一人とは限らない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:17.73,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,It seems he had a companion like Floof.{NOTE:チャモの絵でも仲間がいるみたいだった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:19.65,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,It's as Chief Omna says.{NOTE:オムナ村長の言う通り。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:22.03,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,We need to hurry and meet the Channeler.{NOTE:伝承ジイさんの元へ急ごう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:29.04,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Master Gale! Look there!{NOTE:ゲイル様！あそこは！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:30.45,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,We found them.{NOTE:見つけたか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:50.39,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,What is it, Aptonoth?{NOTE:どうした？アプトノス。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:54.85,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Dan.{NOTE:ダン先輩。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:57.02,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Somebody's gaining on us.{NOTE:近づいてくるやつがいます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.02,0:12:59.19,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,They must be…{NOTE:きっと例の…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:00.98,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,A Black Rider, for sure!{NOTE:ブラックライダーズでしょう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:03.78,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:05.86,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Rathalos!{NOTE:リオレウス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:11.08,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Nya-ow!{NOTE:ニャグゥ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:14.67,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,He must have followed us.{NOTE:追跡してきたんだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:17.13,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Everyone, go ahead.{NOTE:皆は先を急いで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:18.76,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,I will stop him here.{NOTE:ここは俺が食い止めます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:20.26,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Nole!{NOTE:ノール！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:24.47,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Even if he rides a Rathalos, I should delay him with this flash ball!{NOTE:相手がリオレウスでもこの閃光玉でくらくらさせてやりますよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:28.97,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,What's with you?{NOTE:ん？何？お前。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:36.40,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,I'm a Rider from Hakum. I won't let you pass.{NOTE:ハクム村のライダーだ。ここは通さないぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.40,0:13:38.40,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Won't let me pass, huh…{NOTE:通さないって…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:41.24,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Isn't your Monstie an Aptonoth?{NOTE:お前のオトモンそれアプトノスだろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:43.99,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Just like you see.{NOTE:見ての通りだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:47.49,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,An Aptonoth? An Aptonoth against…{NOTE:プトノス？アプトノスで俺の…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:50.08,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,…against my Dusk?{NOTE:俺のダスクを止めようっていうの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:51.50,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Are you for real?{NOTE:マジか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:56.04,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,What a laughing stock, Master Gale.{NOTE:これは笑えますね、ゲイル様！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:13:59.17,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,What's wrong with an Aptonoth.{NOTE:アプトノスの何がおかしい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:04.18,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,It's not worth much, but…{NOTE:どうせ大したものじゃないだろうが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:06.93,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,…hand over your Kinship Stone.{NOTE:お前の絆石をよこせ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.93,0:14:10.68,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Give it obediently and I won't hurt you.{NOTE:素直に渡せば痛い目に遭わずに済むぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:11.89,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me!{NOTE:なめるな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:13.69,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Let's go, Aptonoth!{NOTE:いくぞアプトノス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.69,0:14:15.60,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,You're the one who's underestimating.{NOTE:なめてんのはそっちだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:19.48,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,How was it?{NOTE:どうだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:21.69,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:31.83,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Why the flash ball didn't faze him?{NOTE:何で閃光玉が効かないんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:36.75,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,You're clueless, are you?{NOTE:お前らホント何も知らないのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.93,0:14:47.30,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,What was that?{NOTE:今の何？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:50.01,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,It must've been that Monstie's Dragon Breath!{NOTE:あのオトモンの拡散龍ブレスだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:51.35,Default,Stone,0,0,0,,Nole!{NOTE:ノール！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:52.31,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Stone!{NOTE:ストーン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:54.02,Default,Stone,0,0,0,,Go without me!{NOTE:皆は先に！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:56.85,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,Dan, I'll go as well.{NOTE:ダン先輩俺！も行ってきます！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:03.65,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,What do we do, Dan?{NOTE:どうします？ダン先輩。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.65,0:15:05.11,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,We hurry up.{NOTE:先を急ぐぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:09.49,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,No matter what, we need to bring you to the Channeler!{NOTE:お前たちを何としても伝承ジイさんの元へ送り届ける。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:11.45,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,That's our mission!{NOTE:それが俺たちの使命だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:18.92,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Master Gale! Two people that are not Lute are coming!{NOTE:ゲイル様！リュートじゃないやつが二人向かってきます！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.92,0:15:21.30,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Ha! How persistent!{NOTE:ハッ！懲りもせず！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:24.63,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,Is he the one?{NOTE:あいつか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:29.30,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Hand over your Kinship Stones.{NOTE:お前らの絆石をよこせ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:32.85,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,If you do as I say, I won't hurt you.{NOTE:素直に渡せば痛い目に遭わずに済むぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:34.89,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,What a big shot you think you are.{NOTE:でかい口をたたくんじゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:36.56,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,There's two of us, you know!{NOTE:こっちは二人だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:38.27,Default,Stone,0,0,0,,We'll attack you from both flanks.{NOTE:挟み撃ちにするぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:48.03,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,They really don't know a thing about fighting.{NOTE:こいつらホント戦い慣れしてませんね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:51.20,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Totally.{NOTE:まったくだね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:52.91,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Let's crush them.{NOTE:食らわせてやれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:54.58,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Dragon Breath.{NOTE:拡散龍ブレスだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.59,0:16:06.97,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,After we pass through this cave, we arrive at the Darj Snowfields.{NOTE:この洞窟を抜ければタルジュ雪原だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:08.97,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,We can lose him here.{NOTE:何とか逃げ切れそうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:13.64,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,No, it won't work!{NOTE:いいや、駄目だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:15.77,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,He's caught up onto us!{NOTE:追い掛けてきた！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:17.85,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go into the cave!{NOTE:お前たちは早く洞窟へ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:19.27,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,What about you, Dan?{NOTE:ダン先輩は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:20.69,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!{NOTE:ここは任せろ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:21.77,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go!{NOTE:早く行け！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:23.11,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,But…!{NOTE:だけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.11,0:16:24.90,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Let's go, Lute.{NOTE:行こう、リュート。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:27.82,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Yeah, we need to meet with the Channeler.{NOTE:そうよ。伝承ジイさんに会わないと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:33.37,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,That's it! Navirou will navigate you through the cave!{NOTE:そうだ！ナビルーのナビに従って洞窟を進むのだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:36.50,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,All right then, Dan, we'll be going.{NOTE:じゃあ、ダン先輩。行ってくる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:38.29,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,See you later!{NOTE:行ってきます！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:40.04,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.{NOTE:任せておけ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.21,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Ride On.{NOTE:ライドオン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:45.50,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Qurupeco!{NOTE:クルペッコ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:52.59,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Ah, it's dark!{NOTE:うはっ！暗い！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:54.97,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,I can't navigate like this.{NOTE:これではナビができないぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:57.14,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,Leave it to me here.{NOTE:ここは私に任せて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:59.52,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,Kira-kira-nyaa!{NOTE:キラキラニャ〜ン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:03.48,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,As expected from Fifi.{NOTE:さすがですねティティ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:05.27,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,Let's go.{NOTE:さあ行きましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:09.24,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,It's not Navirou's fault this place is bad to navigate!{NOTE:ナビするナビルーの立場がニャ〜い！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:19.58,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Here comes another weakling Rider.{NOTE:おいおい、またいるよ、弱そうなライダーが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:22.33,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,It's only small fish.{NOTE:身の程知らずばっかりです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:26.50,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,What did you do to my friends?{NOTE:俺の仲間はどうした？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:31.80,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,They're lying beaten up behind.{NOTE:向こうでみんなのびてるよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:34.30,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,You can avoid joining them if you give us your Kinship Stone.{NOTE:絆石さえ奪えば用はない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:36.64,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Don't screw with me.{NOTE:ふざけるな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:40.14,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Isn't that a Qurupeco?{NOTE:お前のオトモンクルペッコじゃないか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:43.85,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Think you can stop us with that?{NOTE:それで俺たちを止められるとでも思ってんの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:46.36,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Don't make fun of Qurupeco.{NOTE:クルペッコをなめるんじゃないぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:50.94,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Qurupeco… Qurupeco…{NOTE:クルペッコはな…クルペッコはな…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:53.49,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Qurupeco is…!{NOTE:クルペッコはな…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:02.37,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,How is it?{NOTE:どうだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:05.13,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Qurupeco can do something like this!{NOTE:クルペッコはこういうことができるんだぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:09.51,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Wah, it just multiplied.{NOTE:うわー、こいつら数だけは揃えましたね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:12.59,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,It's all the same though.{NOTE:だが、しょせん数だけだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:14.55,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Go!{NOTE:行け！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:20.06,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Master Gale!{NOTE:ゲイル様！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:21.68,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,He…!{NOTE:あいつ…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:25.90,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,What?{NOTE:何のまねだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.77,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,I won't let you make any step further.{NOTE:ここは通さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:38.99,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,What was that?{NOTE:何？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:42.12,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Dan must be fighting him now.{NOTE:ダン先輩があいつと戦ってるんだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:44.16,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Let's hurry up.{NOTE:俺たちも急ごう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:45.58,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,How was it?{NOTE:どうだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:47.88,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,You won't be able to follow them now.{NOTE:これでもう通れないぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:50.50,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,You little…{NOTE:てめえ…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:52.42,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Now you've done it!{NOTE:やってくれたな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:55.18,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,There's more where it came from!{NOTE:まだまだ！これからだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.18,0:18:57.39,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,In top form!{NOTE:絶好調！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:02.85,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,How long is this cave anyway?{NOTE:しかしこの洞窟はどこまで続いているんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:05.69,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,We keep on walking and walking and it never ends…{NOTE:行けども行けども果てしニャ〜い…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:11.90,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,There's no doubt that we arrive at the Darj Snowfields at the end though.{NOTE:タルジュ雪原に着くことは間違いないんだろうけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:19.83,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Jeez, you gave me some hard time.{NOTE:ったく面倒かけさせやがって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:22.87,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Looks like we can't proceed any further.{NOTE:この先には行けませんね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:25.71,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,What should we do, Master Gale?{NOTE:どうします、ゲイル様？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:28.17,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Tracking is impossible.{NOTE:追跡は無理だな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:30.63,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,We're returning to the Black Castle.{NOTE:いったんブラックキャッスルに戻るぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:31.88,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Okay.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:52.19,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Dan's group has returned!{NOTE:ダン先輩たちが戻ってきたっす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:20:01.16,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,I heard that rare Rathalos species was tough, but didn't think it was {\i1}that{\i0} tough.{NOTE:リオレウス希少種は強いモンスターと聞いてはいたが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:04.75,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,But that's not all.{NOTE:そればかりではない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:10.29,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,It also has the power of other monsters.{NOTE:他のモンスターの力も備えている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:14.84,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,That's how it is.{NOTE:そういうことだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.84,0:20:18.89,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,That is the power of the Rite of Channeling.{NOTE:それが伝承の儀の力なんじゃよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.89,0:20:25.10,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,It lets a monster use the abilities of another monster.{NOTE:あれはモンスターに別のモンスターの能力を使えるようにするんじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:28.25,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Can you really do such thing?{NOTE:そんなことができるんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:33.82,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Chief Omna. We were robbed of our Kinship Stones.{NOTE:オムナ村長。俺たち絆石を奪われてしまいました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:39.71,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,Why are you going that far?{NOTE:やつは何のためにそんなまねを？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:40.83,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Whew.{NOTE:ハァ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:43.33,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Now I can't use Ride On.{NOTE:これではライダーを名乗れん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:45.08,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,In bad form.{NOTE:絶不調。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:50.92,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,Now the three of us are the only ones in the village that can use Ride On.{NOTE:今村でライドオンできるのは僕たち三人だけなんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.92,0:20:53.37,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,Responsibility became serious-nya.{NOTE:責任重大になったゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:55.95,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,We better do our best.{NOTE:私たちがしっかりしないとね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:58.35,Default,Chamo,0,0,0,,Our best-nya.{NOTE:しっかりするでしゅニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:21:00.62,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Hyoro, Mille.{NOTE:ヒョロ先輩ミル先輩。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:05.26,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,My Monstie is a Velocidrome. Will we any useful?{NOTE:自分のオトモンドスランポスなんですけど大丈夫っすかね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:08.18,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,I don't think so.{NOTE:駄目だと思う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:13.01,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,Mille, you don't need to be so harsh.{NOTE:ミル、そんなはっきり言わなくても。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.01,0:21:15.71,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,It's better to be honest in this case.{NOTE:はっきりしといた方がいいわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:20.61,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,If they appeared here, we must know our chances.{NOTE:もしあいつらが現れたら自分の立ち回りを考えてもらわないとね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:22.01,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,I will do my best!{NOTE:頑張るっす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:25.14,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,When it comes to that, just leave things to me.{NOTE:まっいざとなったら俺に任せな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.71,0:21:34.46,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Master Anvis.{NOTE:アンヴィス様。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:37.31,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,These are the Kinship Stones we've obtained this time.{NOTE:これが今回手に入れた絆石です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:39.31,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Here they are.{NOTE:これでございます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:45.26,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,They're not a big deal, but I hope you can forgive us with these 4.{NOTE:大したやつらじゃありませんでしたが４つあるということでご勘弁を。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:50.01,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,We failed to obtain that Lute's Kinship Stone this time.{NOTE:リュートってやつの絆石は今回取り損ねてしまいましたが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:53.28,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,But we won't next time.{NOTE:次は必ず。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.28,0:21:57.53,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Master Gale, where did that Lute go?{NOTE:ゲイル様、リュートのやつどこ行っちゃったんでしょうね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.49,0:22:11.87,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,You seem to be behaving.{NOTE:おとなしくしているようだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.87,0:22:16.02,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Nuts, make a good meal for this good kid.{NOTE:ナッツ、この良い子ちゃんにうまいものでも作ってやれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.02,0:22:18.90,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Roger.{NOTE:はい。かしこまりました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.90,0:22:22.40,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,A good meal for a good kid.{NOTE:良い子ちゃんにはうまいものですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:33.10,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Oh, it's an exit!{NOTE:おお！出口だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.10,0:22:35.77,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Finally, the Darj Snowfields!{NOTE:ついにタルジュ雪原だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:38.32,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Hurrah! We're here!{NOTE:やった！着いた！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.82,0:22:42.07,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Ah… cold.{NOTE:さ…寒い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:45.16,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,What did you expect snow fields will be like?{NOTE:まっ雪原はこんなものでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.16,0:22:46.91,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Aren't you cold?{NOTE:寒くないのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.91,0:22:48.24,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Not really.{NOTE:別に。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.24,0:22:49.33,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,What about you, Fifi?{NOTE:ティティは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:50.83,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,Hmph!{NOTE:フンッ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.83,0:22:52.41,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,I'll be fine with this.{NOTE:これで大丈夫。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.41,0:22:54.58,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,I'm so jealous.{NOTE:うらやましい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.58,0:22:57.71,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Wait, I'll create us a Hot Mist in a second.{NOTE:待ってて、今ホットミストをかけるから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.88,0:23:03.67,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,You should feel a little warmer with this.{NOTE:はい。これで寒さをしのげるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.67,0:23:07.09,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,N-Nope, it's still cold.{NOTE:う…それでもまだ寒い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.51,0:23:14.73,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,We've arrived at Darj Snowfields, but where is the Riddlemaster's cottage?{NOTE:ここタルジュ雪原なんだろうけど、なぞなぞジイさんの小屋はどこだろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.73,0:23:17.13,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Navirou thinks it's this way.{NOTE:ナビルーはあっちだと思うぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.13,0:23:18.30,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Maybe this way?{NOTE:じゃあこっちか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.30,0:23:19.55,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Nya-ow!{NOTE:ニャグゥ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.61,0:23:25.36,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't leave Navirou behind!{NOTE:こら！ナビルーを置いていくな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.57,0:23:32.03,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Nariki here!{NOTE:自分ナリキ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.03,0:23:36.18,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,I've yet to become a proper Rider, but I won't lose to anybody in motivation!{NOTE:ライダーになりたてっすけどやる気だけは誰にも負けないっす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:39.00,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Eh? A weird guy appears!{NOTE:えっ？何か変なやつが！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:43.92,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Next time, "The Biggest Narcissist Ever!? Mad Appears!" Ride On!{NOTE:次回「空前絶後のナルシスト！？マッド見参！」にライドオン！}
